# Hangman Game

This is a simple text-based Hangman game created using Python.

## Features

- Randomly selects a word from a list of predefined words
- Allows the player to guess one letter at a time
- Maximum 6 incorrect guesses
- Displays correct and incorrect guesses
- Shows the word when the game is over

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Random module
- While loop
- If-else conditions
- Lists
- Strings